With with project you can turn the KL25Z board from Freescale into a joystick that can be used with Flightgear.

Installation
============
1) Copy serialport.xml to Flightgear's Protocol directory.
2) Download flightgear_controller_KL25Z.bin to your KL25Z board or compile the source code in mbed.org and download the binary to the board.
3) Start Flightgear using the start_flightgear.sh script
